@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.31
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.79)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.09) / v2))
    v1 = 0.07
    tmp = (tmp * ((v1 + 0.65 / v0 + 0.59) - (v1 + 0.69 * v1 + 0.47)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v1 + 0.09 - v0 + 0.47)))
    tmp = ((0.34 / (v2 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.40)) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.39 + v0 + 0.98)))
    v2 = 0.28
    tmp = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.96 * tmp + 0.70) + v0))
    data[tid] = v0
